commit.message:
feat: expanded AgentEvent + MessagePartType for rich UI (Phase 1d)

AgentEvent new variants:
- ThinkingStarted { iteration }
- ReasoningDelta/ReasoningComplete (chain-of-thought with duration)
- ContextWarning { level, used_tokens, max_tokens }
- ContextCompacted { freed_tokens, before, after }
- LoopDetected { tool_name, consecutive_count }
- CircuitBreakerTriggered { consecutive_failures, last_tools }
- ExecutionTreeNode { id, parent_id, label, status }
- ExecutionTreeUpdate { id, status, detail }
- MessagePart { part_type } (for AI Elements rendering)

MessagePartType enum (Vercel AI Elements inspired):
- Text, Reasoning, ToolInvocation, CodeArtifact, Source, Suggestion

AgentEventEmitter: 10 new emit methods
AgentHarness::run(): wired thinking_started, tree_node, circuit_breaker, context_warning

All 1,079 tests pass.

